parameters:
\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>Support Succubus Industries! Please support Succubus
Industries!

\nc<Senpai>It's because it's the same as always. But to beat our
competitors, this is the best we can do.

\nc<Senpai>The rival company is new, so they haven't gotten permission
for street advertising yet. The succubus industry is for
adults, so they're very strict about the details.
\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>I see...(As expected, Senpai knows a lot.)

\nc<Senpai>But you're right, doing the same thing as always might not
be good. Maybe it's time to bare some skin.
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>What?! What else am I supposed to take off?!
\nc<Senpai>Didn't you want to try something different from before?
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>I didn't say anything about going that far...

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>What's that? So you'd prefer if we just keep on with the
forced dispatch?
\nc<Saki>Uh...o-okay, I understand. What should I do?

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Don't worry. I won't make you do anything too terrible.
After all, we can't have a live performance on the side of
the road.

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Th-that's right! (Thank goodness. There's still some common
sense in this industry.)

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>We need to catch the customers' eyes with a performance that
our rivals can't easily replicate. And if possible, no
touching...
\nc<Saki>(Wow, is there really such a performance?)

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>I've decided. Saki, we're going to do a photo shoot event
after all.

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Eeeek! In the middle of the street like this?! (She came up
with such an outrageous idea...)

\nc<Senpai>It's fine, it's fine. All Saki has to do is masturbate
normally on the side of the road while the customers take
pictures...

\nc<Saki>No way! What do you mean 'masturbate normally on the side of
the road'? Won't I get arrested for public indecency?

\nc<Senpai>If that law applied, you would have been arrested just for
walking out in that outfit.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>That's true... Our uniforms are pretty much public indecency
level, aren't they.
\nc<Senpai>So there you go, Saki. Do your best!

\nc<Saki>(Ugh, why does it have to be me... And masturbating on the
side of the road, no less...)
\nc<Senpai>If you don't like it, then come up with another idea.

\nc<Saki>Well, I do think it's a good idea for promotion... Sigh, it
always comes to this in the end.
